}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "'''i.connect''' USB 2.0 HUB" is marked on the top of the hub.
"1707V2.0" is silkscreened on the hub's PCB. :The '''Alcor Micro''' hub IC package is marked with "'''ALCOR'''", "AU6254", "M41-JBL-GR", "H76487-5F", and "1218T7F1".
The copyright year on one package is 2012, but the device [http://web.archive.org/web/20101127223650/http://ppa-usa.com/computer-products/usb-hubs/tulip-hub-4-port.html has been on their site for some time] (multiple revisions?).
